OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunshine in the east, otherwise a
OL,7,Fcloudy evening with showery rain
OL,8,Fgradually spreading northeast.
OL,9,FRemaining cloudy overnight with
OL,10,Ffurther showery rain across most
OL,11,Fparts, perhaps briefly heavy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,14,Fscattered showers. The showers mainly
OL,15,Fin the morning before it turns drier
OL,16,Fin the afternoon with some hazy
OL,17,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
